Define Documentation

NAMESPACE

Simple namespace declaration for micro-ROS. This is used to avoid naming conflicts with the other vehicles while still keeping them all under the same ROS_DOMAIN_ID. THIS NEEDS TO MATCH THE ROS 2 NAMESPACE!
